description:
JazzTimes In Person interview with saxophonist/composer/bandleader Steve Coleman from backstage at the 2011 Newport Jazz Festival, presented by Natixis.  In this segment Coleman talks not only about his own role as a mentor to a few generations of jazz musicians, but also about his mentors coming up as a young musician. In addition, Coleman talks about his current band.

This segment is one of several done with musicians who were performing at the 2011 Newport Jazz Festival.

Interview by Lee Mergner. Video by Melissa Mergner.

For more information about JazzTimes magazine, go to jazztimes.com.
